  <summary date="2019-05-29T14:27:30Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Increasing Access to Osteoporosis Testing for Medicare Beneficiaries Act of 2019

This bill specifies that certain Medicare payment rules applicable to imaging services shall apply to dual-energy x-ray absorptiometry services used in bone mass scans beginning in 2019.

The Centers for Medicare &amp; Medicaid Services must establish national minimum payment amounts for such services.</summary>
